{"id": "1002", "question": "A multinational electronics and entertainment conglomerate, founded in 1946 and headquartered in Tokyo, released a product with a removable battery on December 12, 2004. What are the first two letters of the third line of text on the label at the bottom of this product's battery compartment?", "observations": [{"text": "PAGE_TITLE: PSP 1000 Motherboard Replacement - iFixit 维修指南\nPAGE_TEXT: PSP 1000 Motherboard Replacement - iFixit 维修指南 跳转到主内容 修复你的物品 社区 商店 加入维修社区 - 创建账户 PSP 1000 Motherboard Replacement 简介 In this guide I will be going through a detailed step by step process on how to replace your PSP 1000 motherboard. There is no prior experience required in order to begin this replacement as it is very short and simple. The PSP 1000 was first released in 2005 and as many years have passed this device has aged poorly. The main purpose for this guide is to replace a damaged or time worn motherboard that needs replacing as the device itself is ahead of its time, yet the parts have aged 16 years. Have an empty desk along with the tools required for an easy and simple breakdown of your device. Thoroughly read the steps and operate on your device with the specified tools. 你所需要的 步骤 1 Motherboard Remove any external cables from the device and place the device face down on a flat surface. 编辑 添加一条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 2 Remove the battery door cover located on the left hand side. Remove the battery from the device. 编辑 添加一条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 3 Using a flat tool, remove the warranty sticker. Removing this sticker will expose two screws. 编辑 添加一条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 4 Using a Phillips #00 screwdriver, remove the two black 5.2 mm screws marked in red. Remove the two silver 2.4 mm screws marked in orange. Remove the silver 4.4 mm screw marked in yellow at the bottom of the case. Remove the two black 5.4 mm screws marked in green on the back of the case. 编辑 添加一条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 5 Use a plastic opening tool to gently pry the face plate off of the device. Be gentle when prying the face plate as you do not want to crack or scratch it. 编辑 添加一条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 6 Remove the top left and right trigger buttons by simply pulling them out. 编辑 添加一条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 7 Using a plastic opening tool, lift the left side of the bottom circuit that includes the home, start, pause, and volume buttons. 编辑 添加一条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 8 Disconnect the zero-insertion force (ZIF) connector by unlocking the locking tab with a plastic opening tool. 编辑 添加一条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 9 Using a plastic opening tool, lift the LCD screen from in between the metal brackets. Start at the bottom of the screen for an efficient removal. Be very careful as the screen is very fragile. 编辑 1条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 10 Use the plastic opening tool to unlock all the ribbon cables attached from the LCD screen to the motherboard. 编辑 添加一条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 11 Using the Phillips #00 screwdriver, remove the two silver 4.2mm screws marked in red. Remove the three silver 3mm screws marked in orange. Remove the black 4.2mm screw marked in yellow. 编辑 添加一条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 12 Once all screws are removed, gently lift the metal cage from the bottom. If there is resistance, slide the open button on top of the device as it may be latched to the cage. 编辑 添加一条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 13 Note the conductive piece The midframe has a rectangular conductive piece that can fall out and be lost. Without it, the joystick won't work. Make sure to reinsert it so that the contacts on the conductive piece touches the pads. 编辑 添加一条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 14 Remove the single 4.4mm screw that holds the D-Pad in place using the Phillips #00 screwdriver. Underneath the D-Pad, unlock the ZIF connector holding the ribbon cable in place using the plastic opening tool. 编辑 添加一条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 15 Using a plastic opening tool, unlock the small black clip that is located underneath the circuit board. 编辑 添加一条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 16 Using a plastic opening tool, remove the steel bracket under the right trigger. 编辑 添加一条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 17 Use the plastic opening tool to unlock all of the ZIF connectors and disconnect all cables from the motherboard. 编辑 添加一条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 18 Using a plastic opening tool, unclip the cable from the ci", "source_type": "tool_output_text", "channel_id": "source_2", "session_idx": 1, "role": "tool"}, {"text": "PAGE_TEXT: ����\u0000\u0010JFIF\u0000\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0000H\u0000H\u0000\u0000��\u0000C\u0000\u0005\u0003\u0004\u0004\u0004\u0003\u0005\u0004\u0004\u0004\u0005\u0005\u0005\u0006\u0007 \b\u0007\u0007\u0007\u0007\u000f \u0011\u000f\u0012\u0012\u0011\u000f\u0011\u0011\u0013\u0016 \u0017\u0013\u0014\u001a\u0015\u0011\u0011\u0018!\u0018\u001a \u0013\u0017\"$\" $ ��\u0000C\u0001\u0005\u0005\u0005\u0007\u0006\u0007\u000e\b\b\u000e \u0014\u0011\u0014 ��\u0000\u0011\b\u0004�\u0006@\u0003\u0001\"\u0000\u0002\u0011\u0001\u0003\u0011\u0001��\u0000 \u0000\u0000\u0002\u0003\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0001\u0002\u0003\u0004\u0005\u0006\u0007\b��\u0000\u001a\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0001\u0002\u0003\u0004\u0005\u0006��\u0000 \u0003\u0001\u0000\u0002\u0010\u0003\u0010\u0000\u0000\u0001���y=w� s�����T�J�b��J�ZW2n t\u0015N�6�\u0016�6Ms�TM�T � ����K�+-�e��]�N��\u0019�ltt�V�zsCz�T�G6��y�&�\u0017)D\\�E�R��&3x�{L|& �\u0016��O+: D�\u0003\u0004�s�3U�n�E�[W��z[�e� � ���\u0012 ��@�\u0015,�tI.* n�\u0011D�Hj�Wf��gJ�L�.^��U;&��J�\\�e� M�57T��ۖw:��8�YΙ�|�'A`�M�f��]R�,��9>*��|�=}��\u0017K� |��� ܱ\u0012�8:��z�%Kڟ\u0007��� ���Ծ�ܗ��?��>3��v���֩��4}g \u0012}��|�� CG���\u0000������8�:�I̻O�����~o���\u0013 ���-E��N�Hj��!$�\u0004��4FY4\b ����qG���\u001aJ.ί�%�]����GV[�v�z�v��%���Ĩ��Ӎ���,W㲚]t�uS�D!$(4\"!:�\u0005(��\u0014pa��� ~�vy\u0018z~nl\u001