{"id": "1036", "question": "The subsidiary of Sony Group that specializes in its interactive and digital entertainment business operates the PlayStation® platform. In April 2020, this company released a companion controller for its console. The controller's triggers and shoulder buttons have 10-bit linear precision. After turning the controller over, removing the back cover, and taking out the battery, a black baffle can be seen in the middle of the mainboard. Through the cutouts in this baffle, several capacitors for the integrated circuits (ICs) are visible. How many of these capacitors are there in total?", "observations": [{"text": "PAGE_TITLE: Sony DualSense Controller Joystick Cover Replacement - iFixit 维修指南\nPAGE_TEXT: Sony DualSense Controller Joystick Cover Replacement - iFixit 维修指南 跳转到主内容 修复你的物品 社区 商店 加入维修社区 - 创建账户 Sony DualSense Controller Joystick Cover Replacement 简介 Follow this guide to replace the joystick covers on a Sony PlayStation 5 DualSense controller. Note: This guide is for DualSense controllers with an FCC ID ending in 1 . Check the back of your controller to verify your model. If yours ends in A , there will be differences in the internal design, but you can still use this guide. 你所需要的 步骤 1 Unclip the right end of the middle trim Disconnect and power down your controller before you begin. Insert an opening pick underneath the middle trim at the bottom-right corner of the controller to release the clips securing it to the case. 编辑 2条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 2 Unclip the lower-right edge of the middle trim Slide the opening pick along the lower-right edge of the middle trim to release the clips securing it to the case. 编辑 添加一条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 3 Unclip the left end of the middle trim Insert an opening pick underneath the middle trim at the bottom-left corner of the controller to release the clips securing it to the case. 编辑 添加一条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 4 Unclip the lower-left edge of the middle trim Slide the opening pick along the lower-left edge of the middle trim to release the clips securing it to the case. 编辑 添加一条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 5 Remove the middle trim Use your fingers to lift up the bottom edge of the middle trim to release the remaining clips. Lift the middle trim over the joysticks to remove it. 编辑 添加一条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 6 Remove the L1 button With one hand, grip the controller and use your thumb to hold down the left trigger. With your free hand, insert the flat end of a spudger between the L1 and L2 buttons. Use the spudger to gently pry the L1 button away from the controller and remove it, holding your finger over the button so it doesn't eject. 编辑 4条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 7 Remove the R1 button Repeat the previous step to remove the R1 button. 编辑 4条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 8 Remove the rear case screws Use a Phillips screwdriver to remove the two 6.4 mm screws securing the bottom corners of the lower case. 编辑 添加一条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 9 Use a Phillips screwdriver to remove the two 6.4 mm screws behind the L1 and R1 buttons. 编辑 添加一条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 10 Separate the rear case Be gentle when releasing the rear cover clips—they're delicate and can easily break. Use the point of a spudger to release the two clips on either side of the headset jack. 编辑 添加一条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 11 Tight plastic clips secure the left and right edges of the rear case. Insert the flat end of a spudger between the front and rear shells near the bottom of the left edge. Slide the spudger along the left edge and gently pry the shells apart to release the clips. 编辑 2条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 12 Repeat the previous step on the right edge to release its clips. 编辑 添加一条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 13 Lay your controller upside down so the joysticks are on your work surface. Hold the controller down with your fingers and use your thumbs to lift the rear case away from the controller to fully separate it. 编辑 添加一条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 14 Remove the rear case Remove the rear case. 编辑 15条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 15 Disconnect the battery 在这个步骤中使用的工具： Tweezers $4.99 购买 Use a pair of tweezers or your fingers to disconnect the battery from the motherboard. Grip the connector, not the wires, when disconnecting. 编辑 5条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 16 Remove the battery Lift the battery straight out of the battery bracket. 编辑 2条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 17 Remove the lower microphone 在这个步骤中使用的工具： Tweezers $4.99 购买 Grab the lower microphone ribbon cable pull tab with your fingers or a pair of tweezers and disconnect it from the motherboard. 编辑 8条评论 添加一条评论 添加评论 1024 取消 发帖评论 步骤 18 Remove the battery bracket Use a Phillips screwdriver to ", "source_type": "tool_output_text", "channel_id": "source_2", "session_idx": 1, "role": "tool"}, {"text": "PAGE_TEXT: ����\u0000\u0010JFIF\u0000\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0000H\u0000H\u0000\u0000��\u0000C\u0000\u0005\u0003\u0004\u0004\u0004\u0003\u0005\u0004\u0004\u0004\u0005\u0005\u0005\u0006\u0007 \b\u0007\u0007\u0007\u0007\u000f \u0011\u000f\u0012\u0012\u0011\u000f\u0011\u0011\u0013\u0016 \u0017\u0013\u0014\u001a\u0015\u0011\u0011\u0018!\u0018\u001a \u0013\u0017\"$\" $ ��\u0000C\u0001\u0005\u0005\u0005\u0007\u0006\u0007\u000e\b\b\u000e \u0014\u0011\u0014 ��\u0000\u0011\b\u0002X\u0003 \u0003\u0001\"\u0000\u0002\u0011\u0001\u0003\u0011\u0001��\u0000 \u0000\u0000\u0001\u0005\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0002\u0003\u0004\u0005\u0006\u0001\u0007\b��\u0000\u001a\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0001\u0002\u0003\u0004\u0005\u0006��\u0000 \u0003\u0001\u0000\u0002\u0010\u0003\u0010\u0000\u0000\u0001�P\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\