{"id": "1125", "question": "A company, officially established in April 2010, is an internet company with smartphones, smart hardware, and an IoT platform at its core. This company released a smartphone model in December 2020. In April 2021, the well-known teardown and repair organization iFixit published a teardown article on this product. In the article's teardown diagram, what is the color of the illustrated component located to the right of the dark blue illustrated component on the back of the mainboard?", "observations": [{"text": "PAGE_TITLE: Access Denied\nPAGE_TEXT: Access Denied Access Denied You don't have permission to access \"http://www.mi.com/about/index.html\" on this server. Reference #18.863b95b4.1775757361.aaacec https://errors.edgesuite.net/18.863b95b4.1775757361.aaacec", "source_type": "tool_output_text", "channel_id": "source_0", "session_idx": 1, "role": "tool"}], "stats": {"n_source_urls": 3, "n_image_urls": 0, "n_observations": 1}}
